name: 16 iMacs 2001
description: Composite of 16 differently angled photos of Apple iMacs, first and second generation, with various effects, all manipulated in Adobe Photoshop with stock filters. Used as artwork in issue 80 of MACMANIA magazine, published in Brazil in January-February 2001. Created 12-17 January 2001. JPEG file, 1080x1080px.
